skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false

' Actores y Objetos
object Admin
object ":UI\nManualSchedule\nAssignment" as UI
object ":Controller\nManualSchedule\nAssignment" as Controller  
object ":Assignment" as Assignment
object ":UserSubject" as UserSubject
object ":DaySchedule" as DaySchedule
object ":Classroom" as Classroom

' Mensajes numerados - CREAR
Admin --> UI : **1.** Crear
